Shredded my first show of 2023 with the og homie @mitchmckelvey an it just so happened to be at El Diamante High! Was stoked to make a visit back to “The Wall of Champions” and pay tribute to my all time favorite trick.. Flair to Swish🏀 This was definitely one of the most scary/rewarding moments of my life but the setup couldn’t have been more perfect and the energy was flowing heavy that day so you know we had to send it❤️🚲🙌

Stoked to be riding for @reklamationbikes!! Loving the way this new @ajanayalater frame is feeling. Definitely the lightest, most stiff frame I’ve ever built up and it looks amazing! So happy with how it turned out. If you’re looking for a frame that is super lightweight, sturdy, and American made out of OX platinum tubing, give one of these bad boys a try! You won’t regret it ❤️🚲

Excited to share some of what I’ve been working on the past few months! Thankful and honored to have the opportunity to be apart of the reimagined @ringling Bros and Barnum & Bailey “The Greatest Show On Earth” legacy. So stoked to be performing the “Ultimate Playground” act with this dream crew! Thanks to everyone behind the scenes for bringing all of these talented humans together from all around the world to do what we love 🎪❤️🚲

Had such a dialed time shredding @4seasonssk8park while we were in Milwaukee last week! The energy & vibes this place brings is truly something special and so much fun to ride. Literally addicted to how this fresh @reklamationbikes has been feeling👌❤️🚲
